d of illegal structures. It will resume after clear court orders are received.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/gurugrams-anti-encroachment-drive-on-hold-by-hsvp-awaiting-high-court-directions/130568614?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-361566/130568614.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}